                        <interp inst="t18430227-name-1048" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES CUISHAN</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant T</hi> 15.) I took the prisoner—she said she had sixpence-halfpenny, and if it came to more she would pay for it—she put down sixpence-halfpenny on the bacon.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I asked him to weigh it, and he gave me into custody; I am as innocent as a baby.</p>
